    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for simple, affordable wheels that won\u2019t break the bank? This car isn\u2019t perfect and it shows its age, but it\u2019s a solid option for someone who wants basic transportation, a project, or a handy backup vehicle. Plenty of life left for the right buyer, and priced fairly so you can get into something dependable without spending a fortune. If you\u2019re realistic and want good value, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Strong-running project with solid mechanical character and plenty of upside for the next owner. The engine fires up, pulls cleanly, and the drivetrain feels fundamentally serviceable, making this a great candidate for someone who wants an affordable entry point with usable bones. Not a cosmetic showpiece, but it has the kind of honest wear you expect from a budget-friendly driver/project, with good parts value and room to sort and improve over time. If you want something inexpensive with real potential and a platform worth wrenching on, this one makes a compelling case.",
      "price": 6950.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
