      "description": "Budget-friendly and priced to move, this vehicle offers a practical opportunity for a value-focused buyer seeking basic transportation, a project, or an extra car to keep on hand. It shows its age and wear, but it remains an appealing low-cost option for someone who appreciates straightforward value. Offered as an economical choice with plenty of potential.",
