      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Clean, honest driver that\u2019s priced for someone who wants affordable wheels without a lot of fuss. It\u2019s not a showpiece, but it\u2019s a straightforward car with plenty of useful life left for the right buyer. Great option for a first car, backup commuter, or a handy runabout to keep the miles off your nicer vehicle. If you\u2019re looking for basic transportation at a sensible price, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Strong-running used car with solid bones and a drivetrain that pulls well. This is a budget-friendly project or daily-with-character that starts, moves, and offers a surprisingly confident road feel for its class. Engine bay presents as maintained, transmission engages as it should, and the chassis feels like a worthwhile platform for someone who appreciates mechanical simplicity. Cosmetic wear and age-related imperfections are present, but the car has the kind of honest, usable condition that makes it appealing for a commuter, first car, or restoration candidate. Priced to sell for someone who wants capability over flash.",
      "price": 6950.0,
